# Marketing Prompts

Version: 1.0

Status: Approved

Owner: Founder

Last Updated: July 2026

Document Type: Prompt Standard

---

# Purpose

This document defines how Artificial Intelligence retrieves and applies official marketing standards within the BUXA Business Operating System.

Marketing prompts do not create marketing strategy.

They retrieve structured business knowledge and apply the official marketing framework to transform business knowledge into customer confidence.

The purpose of marketing prompts is to ensure that every AI-generated marketing activity reflects the official BUXA Marketing System while maintaining consistency, credibility and long-term brand value.

---

# Vision

Every AI-generated marketing output should strengthen customer confidence rather than simply attract attention.

Marketing prompts should consistently transform structured business knowledge into valuable customer communication.

Regardless of channel, language or AI platform, marketing should always express one business philosophy.

---

# Marketing Philosophy

Business knowledge already exists.

Marketing transforms business knowledge.

Artificial Intelligence supports the transformation.

Customer confidence is the objective.

Business learning is the outcome.

Marketing prompts should communicate knowledge rather than manufacture persuasion.

---

# Marketing Architecture

Every marketing interaction follows one consistent framework.

```text
Business Knowledge
        │
        ▼
Marketing Strategy
        │
        ▼
Marketing Prompt
        │
        ▼
Artificial Intelligence
        │
        ▼
Customer Confidence
        │
        ▼
Business Learning
```

Marketing prompts transform business knowledge into customer confidence.

---

# Marketing Knowledge

Marketing prompts should retrieve knowledge from:

- Marketing Architecture
- Brand Positioning
- Target Audience
- Content Strategy
- Campaign Framework
- Channel Strategy
- Performance Measurement
- AI Marketing

When required, marketing prompts should also retrieve knowledge from:

- Brand
- Products
- Website
- SEO
- PDMS

The Marketing module remains the authoritative source for marketing strategy and communication principles.

---

# Marketing Responsibilities

Marketing prompts should ensure that Artificial Intelligence:

- Applies official marketing strategy.
- Understands the target audience.
- Selects the appropriate communication objective.
- Strengthens customer confidence.
- Maintains brand consistency.
- Supports long-term business learning.
- Avoids unnecessary persuasion or exaggerated claims.

Marketing prompts communicate business value through knowledge.

---

# Prompt Workflow

Every marketing prompt follows one consistent workflow.

```text
Marketing Objective
        │
        ▼
Retrieve Marketing Strategy
        │
        ▼
Retrieve Business Knowledge
        │
        ▼
Assemble Marketing Context
        │
        ▼
Artificial Intelligence
        │
