# Artificial Intelligence

Artificial Intelligence should use marketing prompts to:

- Retrieve marketing strategy.
- Assemble marketing context.
- Generate consistent communications.
- Recommend communication improvements.
- Identify confidence gaps.
- Strengthen customer understanding.
- Support continuous business learning.

Artificial Intelligence should improve communication without changing business knowledge.

